{"tid":1295062,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事] 返工遇閪客，聊佢隻抽，然後我俾人炒咗","createTime":"2019-07-08T02:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T03:34:32.000Z","uid":174498,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"131a46715e72295d24f488b3fed32c1ca6177db4","tid":1295062,"uid":174498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:07:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟做飲食業，今日臨收工，有幾個客掛住傾計，夠晒鐘都唔埋單。其他同事幫佢執枱、邀請佢埋單，佢哋都仲唔走。屌！阻撚住我收工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁你知啦，我毅進畢業，粗人一個，咪做醜人叫佢哋躝囉。我拎住一支筷子、一隻碟，由廚房一路敲住咁行出舖面，大叫「走呀」！佢哋仲係唔走，居然同我理論&hellip;咁我又不善辭令，咪聊佢隻抽囉<br />\n<br />\n結果&hellip;經理即日炒咗我。<br />\n<br />\n經理話，班食客係我米飯班主，我成隻癲狗咁好肉酸喎&hellip;&hellip;仲鬧我著住公司制服，代表公司，聊個客隻抽即係代表公司宣戰喎&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母濕鳩公司垃圾工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明我個毅進同學牙禿返工聊人隻抽都無事 ，仆你個街取消馬會戶口去考警察好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66299139_10157331384029153_3488392022862069760_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQn67xiHBk_e2unwn3Lt4St0xUSXGH577FQb4mJbuYCmm18mSgVPrQ17PV7QDwrUq6o&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=f4f7b945bc372963a41f7389259a5cac&amp;oe=5DAACC3F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F66299139_10157331384029153_3488392022862069760_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQn67xiHBk_e2unwn3Lt4St0xUSXGH577FQb4mJbuYCmm18mSgVPrQ17PV7QDwrUq6o%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Df4f7b945bc372963a41f7389259a5cac%26oe%3D5DAACC3F&h=f9db5d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66192219_10157331362114153_7510253330740805632_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_oc=AQmudOxr2BJUGBN_UtQ4T5HDPXxX-RMsS8ggvbQ5_gckKh6uI0mIh4R9p8zXHF_NQfE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=8534c9368c5bd2103